snippet.title: Henry Halfhead - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist "Henry Halfhead" now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2058140/

Meet Henry! Merely half a head but with the peculiar ability to possess and control any object within their reach. Discover every object's unique properties and abilities and cleverly combine them to progress through Henry's not-so-ordinary everyday life.

• 150+ Playable Objects
• Single-player and Local Co-op
• A Wholesome Story, Told by a Narrator
• Mini-Games

...

Music by Lucien Guy Montandon: https://www.lucienguymontandon.com/

Game by Lululu Entertainment
